In time for the release of iOS 8 we updated imo with awesome new features including: Share: Upload photos videos and links to your contacts and groups directly from apps that support sharing like the Photos app. Today: We added two widgets in the Today panel. The first shows a list of people you have chatted with today so you can quickly chat with them again. With the second widget you can view photos and videos you have received today. Touch ID: With Touch ID on imo you can securely verify sensitive user actions like changing your name.
